column2: SELECT TOP # G.objID, COUNT(N.NeighborObjID) AS pop into mydb.MyTable_# from Galaxy AS G    					    JOIN	Neighbors AS N ON G.objID = N.objID     	    JOIN	Galaxy AS U ON U.objID = N.neighborObjID	    JOIN	photoZ AS Gpz ON G.objID = Gpz.objID		    JOIN	photoZ AS Npz ON U.objID = Npz.objID		 WHERE      G.ra BETWEEN # AND #	     AND G.dec BETWEEN # AND #	      	     AND N.objID < N.neighborObjID 	     AND ABS(Gpz.Z - Npz.Z) < #	     AND (G.flags & (dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&) + dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&) + dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&))) > #  	    AND (G.flags & ( dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&) + dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&) + dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&))) != dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&)           AND (G.flags & (dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&) + dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&))) = #               AND G.petroMag_i > #    AND (G.petroMag_r > # or G.petror5#_r > #)    AND (G.petroMag_r < # AND G.g < # AND G.r < # AND G.i < #)    AND  (G.r < #         AND ( #=# or					              (G.r < (# + (#/#)*(G.g - G.r) +  	 	                              # *(G.r - G.i - # )) 		 	                        AND (( G.r - G.i - (G.g - G.r)/# - #) BETWEEN # AND  # ) 	 AND ((G.r +  	                                                              # * LOG( # * # * G.petror5#_r * G.petror5#_r )) < # )            )         or           (      (G.r < # )          AND (( G.r - G.i -(G.g - G.r)/# -.#) >    	                                	                                (# - #*( G.g - G.r)))  		                                 AND ((G.g - G.r) > ( # + # *(G.r - G.i)))          AND ((G.r  + 	                                         # * LOG( # * # * G.petror5#_r * G.petror5#_r )) < # )         ))  ) GROUP BY G.objID
